<h2 class="bold font-l">Grease opening theme</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Grease is the word! It's got groove, it's got meaning. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AnimatedCreditsOpening" class='trope-example-link'>Animated Credits Opening</a></p>
